Package: ggsegDKwm
Title: Desikan-Killiany White-Matter Parcellation Atlas for the 'ggsegverse' Ecosystem
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R:
    person("Giuseppe", "Barisano", email = "barisano@stanford.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5598-1369"))
Description: Axial Desikan-Killiany white-matter parcellation ('wmparc')
    together with basal-ganglia structures (caudate, putamen, pallidum,
    thalamus), provided as a 'ggseg_atlas' object for use with 'ggseg'.
    Cortical grey matter is merged into a single background label. Built in
    symmetric 'fsaverage_sym' template space with axial slice views.
